        public CustomDimensions set(int dimensionId,
                            java.lang.String dimensionValue)
        This method sets a tracking API parameter dimension%dimensionId%=%dimensionValue%. Eg dimension1=foo or dimension2=bar. So the tracking API parameter starts with dimension followed by the set dimensionId.
        Parameters:
        dimensionId - accepts values greater than 0
        dimensionValue - is limited to 255 characters
        Returns:
        instance of CustomDimensions plugin
